data.description: WELCOME HOME!! This incredible property is located a short driving distance to 377, Western Center Blvd., Basswood Blvd, 35W and 820. The ample living space will greet you with vaulted ceiling and a center facing gas fireplace. Enjoy the privacy of the spacious private formal dining room or an office if you wish. The dining room leads into the updated kitchen, with a view of the spectacular pool. The secondary floor houses the 3 bedrooms, offering the idea floor-plan with the primary bedroom being on the opposite end of the hall. THE HOME QUALIFIES FOR 100% FINANCING THROUGH FIRST FINANCIAL MORTGAGE!
